{"tid":1894430,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"特朗普 : 華府正處理口罩問題 民眾要明白疫症中並無盟友","createTime":"2020-02-24T02:16:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-24T12:06:45.000Z","uid":21470,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"7de724b5677f9679482f490caee656c3e805b70c","tid":1894430,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T02:16:23.000Z","msg":"特朗普：武漢肺炎疫情在美國受控<br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普出訪印度前指，新型冠狀病毒疫情在美國境內仍受控，強調美國擁有世界上最好的醫生，目前只有很少人受感染，未出現死亡個案。他又讚揚國家主席習近平對疫情的處理手法，認為對方非常努力去遏制病毒擴散。<br />\n<br />\n美國至今有35宗確診病例，有美國傳媒引述白宮官員指，白宮最快星期一會向國會申請緊急撥款，應對疫情。美國白宮貿易顧問納瓦羅接受霍士新聞訪問時表示，國內經濟表現強勁，未受疫情影響，目標是將美國的供應鏈，轉回國內，而非集中在中國、印度及歐洲。他又指，華府正處理口罩問題，在疫症中並無盟友，希望民眾明白。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1266457&amp;csid=261_367\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1266457%26csid%3D261_367&d=SulGM1C%2FSMvfI9hDp2hpAnXW3JPDzH8o%2FFP8rJ6jlcg%3D&h=713ef56a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1266457&amp;csid=261_367</a>"},{"pid":"ca0320a362e12c5cdfb9ee9760f563d864bc8f92","tid":1894430,"uid":346806,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T02:17:23.000Z","msg":"在疫症中並無盟友"},{"pid":"ebfb795389a872ade7bf4a0fb879111458c0b0ab","tid":1894430,"uid":170297,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T02:17:38.000Z","msg":"讚揚ccp<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁撚串<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97e17c63a0bd0fb09fb0330c046227c6f42314da","tid":1894430,"uid":267955,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T02:18:17.000Z","msg":"無盟友，呢句係金句<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38dcff4d45ce89863e2f2080c4a335